### TIKWALL6 Script Bundle
/system script
add comment="Initial preparation step of TIKWALL for IPv6: Create/Enable MINFWALL rules. They allow minimal set of incoming traffic (SSH, but can be configured further) and al\
    l outgoing traffic, but block forwarding until the rest of the firewall is loaded." name=TIKWALL6_0_MINFWALL policy=read,write source="####################################\
    ###########################################\
    \n# TIKWALL6 v. 0.1\
    \n# Project home: https://github.com/atsonkov/tikwall\
    \n###############################################################################\
    \n# Copyright 2015 Atanas Tsonkov\
    \n# Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (the \"License\");\
